          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Come on. Ooh, yeah.&lt;br /&gt;
Never be the same again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I call you up whenever things go wrong.&lt;br /&gt;
You&#039;re always there. You are my shoulder to cry on.&lt;br /&gt;
I can&#039;t believe it took me quite so long.&lt;br /&gt;
To take the forbidden step.&lt;br /&gt;
Is this something that I might regret?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(Come on, come on)&lt;br /&gt;
Nothing ventured nothing gained. &lt;br /&gt;
(You are the one)&lt;br /&gt;
A lonely heart that can&#039;t be tamed.&lt;br /&gt;
(Come on, come on)&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;m hoping that you feel the same.&lt;br /&gt;
This is something that I can&#039;t forget.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I thought that we would just be friends.&lt;br /&gt;
Things will never be the same again.&lt;br /&gt;
