Never be the same again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now I know that we were close before.&lt;br /&gt;
I&#039;m glad I realised I need you so much more.&lt;br /&gt;
And I don&#039;t care what everyone will say.&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s about you and me.&lt;br /&gt;
And we&#039;ll never be the same again.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I thought that we would just be friends (oh yeah).&lt;br /&gt;
Things will never be the same again. (Never be the same again)&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s just the beginning it&#039;s not the end. (We&#039;ve only just begun)&lt;br /&gt;
