The US to UK, NYC to LA.&lt;br /&gt;
From sidewalks to highways.&lt;br /&gt;
See it&#039;ll never be the same again.&lt;br /&gt;
What I&#039;m sayin&#039;&lt;br /&gt;
My mind frame never changed &#039;til you came rearranged.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But sometimes it seems completely forbidden.&lt;br /&gt;
To discover those feelings that we kept so well hidden.&lt;br /&gt;
Where there&#039;s no competition.&lt;br /&gt;
And you render my condition.&lt;br /&gt;
Though improbable it&#039;s not impossible.&lt;br /&gt;
For a love that could be unstoppable.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But wait.&lt;br /&gt;
A fine line&#039;s between fate and destiny.&lt;br /&gt;
Do you believe in the things that were just meant to be?&lt;br /&gt;
When you tell me the stories of your quest for me.&lt;br /&gt;
Picturesque is the picture you paint effortlessly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And as our energies mix and begin to multiply.&lt;br /&gt;
Everyday situations, they start to simplify.&lt;br /&gt;
So things will never be the same between you and I.&lt;br /&gt;
We intertwined our life forces and now we&#039;re unified.&lt;/p&gt;

